<Layout title="Nardelli">
	<h1>Welcome</h1>

	<p>
		Welcome to <strong>Nardelli Nespolo</strong>, a homely escape on the Tuscan–Umbrian border. We hope you enjoy everything Umbria and Tuscany have to offer — and that the house makes a perfect base for exploring the area at your own pace.<br><br>
		We want everyone who stays at Nardelli to have a wonderful experience and to fall in love with this corner of Italy the way we have.<br><br>
		Nardelli was built by <strong>Billy McCarthy</strong> back in <strong>19XX</strong>, and it became a place that Billy and his partner <strong>Des</strong> truly cherished. They shared it generously with friends and family, and guests were always welcomed with open arms.<br><br>
		Billy passed away in <strong>2016</strong>, but the house was left to the wider family to continue enjoying and sharing. We’ve all grown very fond of Nardelli and the surrounding area — and we hope you will too.
	</p>

